---
/**
 * Social proof section — community stats + testimonials.
 * Keep numbers honest and update as real data comes in.
 */
---

<section class="wbc-social-proof">
  <div class="wbc-social-proof__inner">
    <h2 class="wbc-social-proof__heading">Trusted by weekend planners everywhere</h2>
    
    <div class="wbc-social-proof__stats">
      <div class="wbc-stat">
        <span class="wbc-stat__number">16+</span>
        <span class="wbc-stat__label">Curated Guides</span>
      </div>
      <div class="wbc-stat">
        <span class="wbc-stat__number">200+</span>
        <span class="wbc-stat__label">Products Reviewed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="wbc-stat">
        <span class="wbc-stat__number">100%</span>
        <span class="wbc-stat__label">Family Tested</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wbc-social-proof__testimonials">
      <div class="wbc-testimonial">
        <p class="wbc-testimonial__text">"Finally, a site that doesn't just list gear — it tells you exactly how to use it for a real weekend with your family."</p>
        <span class="wbc-testimonial__author">— Weekend reader</span>
      </div>
      <div class="wbc-testimonial">
        <p class="wbc-testimonial__text">"The game night guide saved our Friday. We bought the exact kit and had the best time we've had in months."</p>
        <span class="wbc-testimonial__author">— Happy parent</span>
      </div>
      <div class="wbc-testimonial">
        <p class="wbc-testimonial__text">"Love that every guide comes with a budget-friendly option. Not everything has to cost a fortune to be fun."</p>
        <span class="wbc-testimonial__author">— Outdoor enthusiast</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wbc-social-proof__badges">
      <span class="wbc-badge">🏕️ Real family tested</span>
      <span class="wbc-badge">💰 Budget-friendly picks</span>
      <span class="wbc-badge">📦 Amazon Prime eligible</span>
      <span class="wbc-badge">🔄 Updated regularly</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wbc-social-proof {
    background: #f8f6ea;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8dfd3;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8dfd3;
  }
  .wbc-social-proof__inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .wbc-social-proof__heading {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #2c2c2c;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .wbc-social-proof__stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .wbc-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .wbc-stat__number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #CC5500;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .wbc-stat__label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #6b5c4c;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .wbc-social-proof__testimonials {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .wbc-testimonial {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .wbc-testimonial__text {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .wbc-testimonial__author {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #999;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .wbc-social-proof__badges {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .wbc-badge {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8dfd3;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4a3f35;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .wbc-social-proof__stats { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .wbc-stat__number { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  }
</style>
